  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become an abstract artist, working out of a warehouse studio at the top of a skyscraper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/b8f5bb94a1654520cb6fa76fcbec1066.poster.avif?t=1774074415\" aria-label=\"studio sim raycast the wall to paint\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/b8f5bb94a1654520cb6fa76fcbec1066.webm?t=1774074415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/b8f5bb94a1654520cb6fa76fcbec1066.mp4?t=1774074415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform your studio into a personal gallery in this relaxing first-person art game. Create paintings by layering and positioning stickers, then hang your finished works on the walls. No pressure, no timers- just you and your studio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/3db1a7c746e20be74914e436845b69f8.poster.avif?t=1774074415\" aria-label=\"studio sim rotate 2d sprite before placing\" width=494 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/3db1a7c746e20be74914e436845b69f8.webm?t=1774074415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/3db1a7c746e20be74914e436845b69f8.mp4?t=1774074415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Layer, position, and arrange stickers to match target compositions, or make your own abstract compositions-- earning money to unlock strange new stuff while exploring contemporary abstraction in a new virtual form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/2ba4f556370e401331532ff6427c2510.avif?t=1774074415\" alt=\"ui of studio sim\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hang your finished works in the gallery and invite visitors to come and react to your work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/19b94d4ebd7ecc7945ecd91004ba0e8a.avif?t=1774074415\" alt=\"rich boy in studio sim\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become an abstract artist, working out of a warehouse studio at the top of a skyscraper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/b8f5bb94a1654520cb6fa76fcbec1066.poster.avif?t=1774074415\" aria-label=\"studio sim raycast the wall to paint\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/b8f5bb94a1654520cb6fa76fcbec1066.webm?t=1774074415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/b8f5bb94a1654520cb6fa76fcbec1066.mp4?t=1774074415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform your studio into a personal gallery in this relaxing first-person art game. Create paintings by layering and positioning stickers, then hang your finished works on the walls. No pressure, no timers- just you and your studio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/3db1a7c746e20be74914e436845b69f8.poster.avif?t=1774074415\" aria-label=\"studio sim rotate 2d sprite before placing\" width=494 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/3db1a7c746e20be74914e436845b69f8.webm?t=1774074415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/3db1a7c746e20be74914e436845b69f8.mp4?t=1774074415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Layer, position, and arrange stickers to match target compositions, or make your own abstract compositions-- earning money to unlock strange new stuff while exploring contemporary abstraction in a new virtual form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/2ba4f556370e401331532ff6427c2510.avif?t=1774074415\" alt=\"ui of studio sim\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hang your finished works in the gallery and invite visitors to come and react to your work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278180/extras/19b94d4ebd7ecc7945ecd91004ba0e8a.avif?t=1774074415\" alt=\"rich boy in studio sim\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
